<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, March 12 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 4,124.11 on Friday, up 35.50 points,
or 0.87 percent, from Thursday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was heavy with the turnover reaching 110 trillion
Turkish liras (307 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index rose 52.70 points, or 0.98 percent, to
close at 5,493.14; the industrial index increased 21.92 points, or
0.80 percent, to close at 2,741.99; and the services index climbed
37.71 points, or 0.71 percent, to close at 5,405.74. 
</P>
