the eighth congregation of the Institute of Teacher Education at
Kyambogo main campus here, a press release from the President's
Office said.
</P>
<P>
He said that education reform is essential in order to improve
the quality of education and make it more relevant to the needs of
the population and the ever changing environment.
</P>
