training at all levels, Museveni said he is glad that the
institute has expressed its positive response to the education
reform policy by continuously reviewing curricular and syllabi at
different levels as well as introducing new programs and
innovations to social needs.
</P>
<P>
He further reaffirmed the government's total commitment to
universal primary education as an essential ingredient for
national development and modernization.  
