arrest warrant for the two men in 1993.
</P>
<P>
Bai and Zhong fled to Ukraine in 1993 and continued their
criminal activities until their eventual arrest.
</P>
<P>
The official noted that the Ministry of Public Security will
continue to battle criminal activities and strengthen cooperation
with foreign law enforcement agencies. 
