<HEADLINE> Malaysia Urges Development of Domestic Tourism </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, March 13 (Xinhua) -- The Malaysian government
Saturday called upon the private sector to cooperate with it to
develop and promote domestic tourism to help revive the economy.
</P>
<P>
