and Travel Agents is being attended by 107 exhibitors including
representatives of travel and tour agents, airlines, hotels,
resorts and theme parks from Australia, Canada, China, China's
Hong Kong Special Administrative Region, Egypt, India, Indonesia,
Macao, Madagascar, Singapore, South Korea, South Africa, Thailand,
