during cross examination by defense counsel, Thabang Khauoe, SAPA
said.
</P>
<P>
Khauoe asked Mosakeng if the priests who visited the troops
could be identified. Mosakeng said the matter was still under
investigation.
</P>
<P>
Mosakeng and several other senior officers were forced to
resign in September last year.  
